<br>
She would not make herself known to him just yet, she stood and watched until he sat back as his gifts were layed out. She smiled and in a whirl of golden fire. . .she appeared.<br>
<br>
&quot;Your pressence and gifts are welcome at my temple Bellerophon.&quot; She smiled looking down.<br>
<br>
&quot;But what brings you here?&quot;<br>
<br>
She knew what he was seeking, but she let him speak himself. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/umobellerophon.showPublicProfile?language=EN>MO Bellerophon</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=IMG SRC="http://www.helicon.i-p.com/bellerophon-010.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 17<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(8/6/01 1:03 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=130.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Was he dreaming?</span><hr size=1> Bellerophon looked up at the goddess Athena as she appeared before him.He wasn't sure if this were real or if he were dreaming,but respectfully,he stood up and bowed.<br>
<br>
&quot;This is an honor.&quot;He spoke before straightening up.<br>
<br>
&quot;Great Goddess of Wisdom,I wish to tame the wild Pegasus.I have a journey to make,a beast to slay for the people of Lycia.I come to obtain the knowledge of how I can accomplish this.Will you help me?&quot; <p>-=¤ Bellerophon ¤=-</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=goddessathena>Goddess Athena</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 24<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(8/6/01 12:50 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=130.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Pegasus</span><hr size=1> She smiled lightly at his request. She brought her hand to her chin as if to think then looked back down at him.<br>
<br>
&quot;You ask much Bellerophon. No man has ever been able to tame such a creature. Pegasus is a sacred animal. Why would I bestow you this gift?&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/umobellerophon.showPublicProfile?language=EN>MO Bellerophon</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=IMG SRC="http://www.helicon.i-p.com/bellerophon-010.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 18<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(8/6/01 2:34 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=130.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Pegasus</span><hr size=1> &quot;The people of Lycia are of threat from the beast Chimera.I've taken up the challenge to rid the people of this threat.With Pegasus,I can accomplish this.&quot;He bowed his head slightly.<br>
<br>
&quot;With or without your help Goddess Athena,&quot; He then looked back at her. &quot;...I will face this beast.For the people of Lycia.&quot;<br>
<br>
He stood tall,his head held high.He did not fear the concept of going up against the Chimera,infact he was happy he was given the opportunity to destroy the beast.And with Pegasus,he knew he could accompish this task.<br>
<br>
 <p>-=¤ Bellerophon ¤=-</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=goddessathena>Goddess Athena</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 25<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(8/7/01 10:54 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=130.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> To tame the wild horse</span><hr size=1> Athena smiled lightly at his answer.<br>
<br>
&quot;Bellerophon, you see yourself as a worthy warrior in the Goddess's Temple. Behold, I am that Goddess of War, she who sprang from the head of Zeus. They who prove themselves worthy in the sight of me, shall be shown great in the eyes of the Mortals. Asleep? Nay, wake. Here is what will charm the steed you covet.&quot; <br>
<br>
She vanished once more in a whirl of golden light. And Bellerophon was asleep once more. And when he woke, he would find the charm of gold resting in his palms. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/umobellerophon.showPublicProfile?language=EN>MO Bellerophon</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=IMG SRC="http://www.helicon.i-p.com/bellerophon-010.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 19<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(8/18/01 11:55 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=130.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://hometown.aol.com/alteredsoulsx/images/bellerophon-2.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> He Awoke...</span><hr size=1> Bellerophon awoke the next morning and knew of what he had to do in order to tame the wild Pegasus,as he went to stand he realized the object which lay beside him.Quickly he stood and gathered the golden object in his hands,a satisfied smile upon his lips.Before leaving the temple,he looked up and quietly thanked Athena for her guidence.<br>
<br>
Leaving the temple,he goes to his horse then he slipped the golden bridle into his saddle bag,once making sure it was secure.He mounted his black steed,and kicked it into a gallop.He was on his way.<br>
<br>
